          "date": "2015-04-19 13:03:14.000000000",
          "tz": -420
        },
        "subject": "LU-6479 lod: free the striped object immediately",
        "message": "LU-6479 lod: free the striped object immediately\n\nThe master object of striped directory should be\nfreeed immediately once its reference count reach\nto 0, so all of its sub-stripes objects can be released.\n\nOtherwise if one of sub stripe if set with BANSEE flag,\nand master object is kept in cache, then the sub stripe\nwill not be released until the master object is freed.\nThen other threads trying to get this object might be\nhang in lu_object_find().\n\nSigned-off-by: wang di <di.wang@intel.com>\nChange-Id: Iea54db80d263ab91329f11c93b8b8dc9400a39d6\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
